{"tid":1882670,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍區去睇左幾間，都冇switch","createTime":"2020-02-16T11:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T12:46:15.000Z","uid":349418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3b0404451d636cc048fffc0ae9e908b85eeaac35","tid":1882670,"uid":349418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:43:57.000Z","msg":"放成個幾兩個月，諗住買番部switch黎玩下都好。<br />\n去左Aeon黃埔 九龍灣都冇，得switch lite<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃埔豐澤都冇貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又去左game square，人地直程寫著sold out。<br />\n之後去左深水埗間G point，講左請問兩隻字，未講完人地就話switch冇貨啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後好灰咁去對面黃金商場，一入去就見到間金源，行左兩圈見到冇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就去睇下Misonin，條友話switch連兩部濕鳩遊戲39xx，我睬佢都on9，唔好去搶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後去番金源對出果間，問左2880<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依家放棄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搶唔過大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b7f9811121d7ad63b80d8928053b26899183a8","tid":1882670,"uid":53254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"冇貨好耐了 清"},{"pid":"884faeb7f2fc40f02a0fb12f4147dc87cedafb62","tid":1882670,"uid":168509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:15:00.000Z","msg":"我又係見放咁耐假想買部玩下<br />\n去左新城市搵都無哂貨<br />\n新嘅又環等大陸開番先有<br />\n開番都無假放啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇黎都係玩番ps4算..."},{"pid":"52f2b62e5d5606a7930e3cd5f3ce4e7968280a9c","tid":1882670,"uid":349418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1b7f9811121d7ad63b80d8928053b